name: TheVoiceMemoGirl
0:
”Alexa, what's my Flash Briefing?”
”Alexa, play my Flash Briefing”
skdetail:
Flash Briefing Skill
This skill contains: dynamic content.
des:
Wake up and start your day with a positive Voice Memo from your girl, Rachel! 
You never know what you're gonna get, a bit of funny, maybe a punch of motivation or GIRL power!

Just a girl and her phone, sending out positive vibes and energy into your day. 
A voice to inspire you to live a good life, one day at a time. 
Sometimes you just need that someone to help you change your energy and help you see the positive and good in all things. 

Listen everyday for a quick pick me up, when you are setting your daily intentions or just to have a positive voice in your ear.
